<br>
i'd say get 10 points and get purge.  purge has immense utility both in pve and rvr, especially given the number of SI mobs and doden's mobs and such that have magical abilities such as 90 point dots and 40 minute diseases.  and purge is so uber in rvr it's just absurd.  with the nerfing of mcl and fa you really dont have any low cost RAs that will make that serious an impact on your exping.<br>
<br>
either that or get fa 1 and 2 so you can start saving for IP.  it's better to get IP and purge first IMO, for psychological reasons.  if you wait to rank 4+ to start saving for something big it's going to be WEEKS of frustration waiting to save the points.  it nearly drove me nuts saving 3 points for aug dex 2 so then i could AGAIN save yet longer for friggin mop1.  but i was in the middle of rank 5 at the time, GD points are slow.  SO much easier on your mind to save for 1 pointers like aug con 1.  what i truly dread is the six points i need for my next RA which is empty mind, i'm 6,6 currently with zero saved.  six points is like 500,000 rps now.  <!--EZCODE EMOTICON START :( --><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/intl/aenglish/images/emoticons/frown.gif ALT=":("><!--EZCODE EMOTICON END--> <br>
